name: "get rich(ardus) or die trying"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.

"get rich(ardus) or die trying" is Ricardus joining the evol gang and seems that he is moving from the west coast to phoenix. This is the 5th edition of the collection and is for the #EVOLARTCOMP
